{"tid":1287779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樹仁大學副校監向師生發電郵　對衝擊立法會感心憂神傷","createTime":"2019-07-05T10:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T10:52:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a450890581eb6ff2bb485a52865eeb872133f1b2","tid":1287779,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:51:46.000Z","msg":"樹仁大學副校監胡懷中發電郵給全體師生，指近幾周社會運動空前浩大，標誌著香港人為熱愛的土地努力發聲，當中許多年輕人勇於表達意見，爭取理想及公義，學校一貫欣賞支持。但對於7月1日示威者衝擊立法會一事，感到心憂神傷。<br />\n<br />\n胡懷中指出，暴力從不是解決問題的方法，若現階段只停留於重申立埸，諉過指責，於是無補。<br />\n<br />\n他期望社會各界應放下成見，柔乾身段，以對話溝通尋求出路，走出當下香港困局，又期望同學可作出利眾利己、無悔青春的抉擇。"},{"pid":"7b16625807f9503b70139c6e3d5e9987b9e0678f","tid":1287779,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvSJXSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvSJXSZ.png&h=0386e4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}